description:
Keep your gear exactly where you want it, from your driveway to your destination. From lashing your boat to your roof rack, to cinching down your SUP on your cabin top, these burly straps get the job done.

  • Rubberized buckle armour helps protects your car
  • Color coded elasticized loop keeps extra webbing keeps the strap's tail organized
  • Aluminum buckle has been nickel plated to protect it against salt water
  • Breaking strength of 200 kg
name: Level Six 4m (13 ft) Webbing Tie-Down Strap
